Also MMC5 as I recall has no fixed bank. Also when doing MMC5 PRG switching remember there is a PRG-RAM and PRG-ROM involved. I believe bit 7 has to be set to point to ROM rather than PRG-RAM for the area 8000$ to $DFFF. $6000 is always RAM and $E000 is always ROM I think.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1726">MottZilla</a> — Fri May 01, 2009 12:07 pm</p><hr />
