By default the MMC5 swaps the last 8k of PRG ROM at $8000, $a000, $c000 and $e000. From there you have to make some code to configure your bankswitching sheme yourself.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Fri May 01, 2009 1:08 am</p><hr />
